data.description: Quiet, Cul-De-Sac Location! 1 story, brick front, 3/2 with unique interior features of arched passageways, art/deco nooks, high ceilings, finished out garage, new garage door opener, workbench & partially floored attic for seasonal storage. Large family room accentuates the open floor plan feel from the kitchen, breakfast area & breakfast bar. Formal dining area for family gatherings. Split bedroom plan for adult privacy. Spacious master bedroom suite features 2 lavatories, garden tub, separate shower, walk-in closet & private commode closet. Larger than most (cul-de-sac) lot has a privacy fenced backyard with added 12x11 deck. Black appliance package in the kitchen. Refrigerator, washer & dryer can convey. Survey saves money. Easy in/out to I-35 or Easterly route on Fm-150. Close proximity to weekly shopping, schools and city parks.
